cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD 

This paper is about developing a machine translation system using a Recurrent Neural Network, which falls under the category of Natural Language Processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the use of TensorFlow and OpenNMT sequence modeling tool suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of neural networks also suggests that the paper may fall under the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper involves the evaluation of the translation system using a specific metric, which suggests that it may also fall under the category of Software Engineering (cs.SD).
